[4] Cholera - Afghanistan
Date: Wed 15 Feb 2017
Source: WHO, Weekly Epidemiological Record (WER) [edited]
http://www.who.int/wer/en/


Although not publicized in the lay press or in WHO Disease Outbreak Reports, substantial numbers of cases of cholera have been reported to WHO from Afghanistan.

Year / Total Cases / Deaths / CFR (percent)
2012 / 12 / 0 / 0
2013 / 3957 / 14 / 0.35
2014 / 45 481 / 4 / 0.01
2015 / 58 064 / 8 / 0.01

The total 2016 numbers have yet to be reported by WHO. In 2014 and 2015, relatively silently, this country had more cholera cases reported than any other.

